Subject: [PATCH 0752/2066] soc: renesas: Add r8a7793 SYSC PM Domain Binding
 Definitions

upstream a6171412725e4e7e510a2b91a1d79dbc2ef0e679 commit

R-Car M2-N is identical to R-Car M2-W w.r.t. power domains, so reuse the
definitions from the latter.

